This is the letter I have just sent to video complaint , I hope it will be taken up.

Dear Sir,

I am a regular viewer of Nayaltel English movies channel on cable.

I have complained twice, but to no avail.

There used to be 2 NMX good quailty English movies channel , which used to show latest movies too.
Then there was HBO, then filmmax, although Hindi translation, but good stuff.

The down fall of your cable began , by first removing NMX , and replacing it with a bad quality music channel. I fail to understand, who gives you feedback to bring channels ,without looking at market demand and customers too.

Your cable should cater to all types of customers, and you know it too , English movies ,Hollywood movies are in demand.
Already there are many music channels, so this was a foolish move.
Then filmMax was replaced by A1 channel showing Chinese shows, dubbed in urdu
Who watches them?
I know many people with nayatel, in my area, F11, and none of them watches it.

And dubbing English movies in Urdu in one channel is more than enough, why have so many?Why watch English movies dubbed in Urdu?What's the point then.

My firm demand is to restore the other NMX CHANNEL, and restore HBo.
If not bring other quality movie channels
Like Hallmark and many others.

I hope listening to costumers' demands, you will do the needful , and not to make such drastic changes which damages your repute
